text: Susan Allen (May 10, 1951 - September 7, 2015) was an American harpist. She was born in Monrovia, California. Allen died from brain cancer on September 7, 2015 in Seattle, Washington. She was 64. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1951 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Deaths from brain cancer Category:Cancer deaths in Washington (state) Category:Musicians from California
